  <brief_title>Phase II Cisplatin + Temozolomide in Malignant Glial Tumours in Children and Adolescents</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Study of the Combination of Cisplatin + Temozolomide in Malignant Glial Tumours in Children and Adolescents at Diagnosis or in Relapse</official_title>
  <sponsors>
